  "texts": [
    "In summary of the above analysis and discussion, this study further explores methods for dataset generation building upon prior research.",
    "Firstly, images are manually obtained and processed using advanced tools such as Photoshop to acquire high-quality image data.",
    "Secondly, image generation is conducted using ChatGPT and the Stable Diffusion model.",
    "Detailed textual descriptions are generated using ChatGPT, and subsequently, images matching these descriptions are generated through the application of the Stable Diffusion model, thereby expanding the dataset.",
    "Finally, real railway data from the Railsem19 28 dataset is combined with random image augmentation and the CDTNet 29 method to synthesize foreign objects."
  ],
